Column layouts enable content to display on each device in the most effective way possible. You will see content adapt automatically in order to remain user friendly and beautiful regardless of the device they are using to access it.

Display conditions allow authors to easily create device-specific content, or content based on the value of a project variable. Want to display a detailed graphic for a desktop display and a simplified readable version for smaller mobile screens? No problem.
